{"tid":2514384,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"中國拌飯砸4億置入《文森佐》！宋仲基道歉　中國網友罵翻","createTime":"2021-05-03T08:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T08:39:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63a06b98a9915d763bae644892fdd13b622f4081","tid":2514384,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:32:28.000Z","msg":"廠商將商品置入到戲劇當中，在如今已是相當正常，只不過在韓劇中看到中國商品，卻讓人覺得怪怪的。韓劇《黑道律師文森佐》在第8集當中，安排男主角宋仲基吃中國出產的拌飯，讓韓國人覺得相當突兀，在網上罵翻，紛紛要求下架。針對此爭議，宋仲基今（3）日受訪時道歉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/05/03/3137855-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2F3137855-PH.jpg&h=56db40b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宋仲基在劇中飾演文森佐。（圖／Netflix提供）<br />\n<br />\n先前中國、韓國才因為「泡菜」引起兩國人民網路舌戰，一名韓國吃播主Hamzy因認同「泡菜是韓國食物」竟遭到中國網友出征，被指控是「辱華」慘遭中國平台解約。沒想到不久後，雙方又因「拌飯」引發爭議，挑動中韓敏感神經。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/bleuchatte?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1371282062108360708%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.setn.com%2Fnews%2F933851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbleuchatte%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1371282062108360708%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.setn.com%252Fnews%252F933851&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=2c76658e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/bleuchatte?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1371282062108360708%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.setn.com%2Fnews%2F933851</a><br />\n▲《文森佐》中出現中國拌飯，引發爭議。<br />\n《黑道律師文森佐》第8集當中，男主角坐在辦公室低頭吃泡菜拌飯，更大讚食物很好吃，鏡頭轉到這碗拌飯，上面清楚寫著「自嗨鍋」，似乎有些突兀。原來這是中國餐飲品牌「自嗨鍋」的自熱式拌飯，據韓國媒體報導，「自嗨鍋」砸下韓幣3、4億元（約新台幣750萬至1000萬元），在《文森佐》中曝光4集。可沒想到畫面曝光後，立刻引來大批韓國網友不滿，網上輿論沸騰，要求刪除該爭議片段。最後劇組在3月31日宣布，會將畫面全數刪除，一點也不留。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/05/03/3137843-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2F3137843-PH.jpg&h=25cbc69f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宋仲基在劇中吃中國拌飯，引發爭議。（圖／Netflix提供）<br />\n<br />\n針對此爭議，根據韓媒《머니투데이》今日報導，宋仲基表示，站在演員的立場上，萌生了要一起商議會更好的想法。他表示，因為電視劇外的爭議，讓自己更想努力提升電視劇的內在，如果有人因為中國置入爭議而感覺到失望，他會透過電視劇本身的魅力再次獲得觀眾的信任。不過，宋仲基也對此道歉，表示因為置入廣告而感到失望的人有很多，「我認為作為主演應該向大家道歉」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/05/03/3137885-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2F3137885-PH.jpg&h=c874415d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲中國網友罵翻了。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n該新聞一出，再度引發中國網友不滿，紛紛表示，「為什麼道歉，吃了中國拌飯就是中國人了？」、「韓國人真的腦子&hellip;」、「極度自卑的民族」、「哈哈哈，韓國人好好笑啊」、「韓國人好玻璃心~~」、「極度的自卑才會造就莫名其妙的自尊心，沒錯，就是韓國人」、「？這也要道歉？」"},{"pid":"7066087f7ac3f0e34523e47cb28c6b1f24a02f95","tid":2514384,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:33:48.000Z","msg":"屌&hellip;嗨左幾集變咗食糖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臭支撚"},{"pid":"7acf5dbd293f575b804330a60333ace0af58682b","tid":2514384,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7066087f7ac3f0e34523e47cb28c6b1f24a02f95","tid":2514384,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:33:48.000Z","msg":"屌&hellip;嗨左幾集變咗食糖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臭支撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:34:55.000Z","msg":"唔睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229571a69e50fc0d9fbc16d1db3a328bb60b89bc","tid":2514384,"uid":145854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"你老味<br />\n連睇幾套韓劇都有呢個自閪鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d495e5369607f748add75bfaf38b9a784c3b430b","tid":2514384,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"229571a69e50fc0d9fbc16d1db3a328bb60b89bc","tid":2514384,"uid":145854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"你老味<br />\n連睇幾套韓劇都有呢個自閪鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"反韓劇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd289153a70b8205868ec000e8caaa1704764945","tid":2514384,"uid":60023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"大陸狗邏輯<br />\n道歉係自大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}